channel.title: Wont connect
channel.description: Hey guys ive had a server for about a week and a half ish and its been working well ... then i went out 1 day and for some reason server stopped working even when i came back home the next day i tried to log in and says error connecting to server i tried to guirun and run server under source nothing happens i dont know wat the problem is if i did i can do try to figure it out but idk wat it is .... when irun server says its online but no1 can connect for some reason .... this happen to anyone? got any solutions? please let me know =[

item.title: Wont connect
item.dc:creator: @xxbanditxx xxbanditxx
item.description:
@xxbanditxx wrote:

[quote=“fleminmj01, post:4, topic:406194”]your ip adress may have changed. mine used to all the time. you have to open up command promp (cmd) and type in ipconfig.
find where is says IPv4. then open ur browser and go to ur portforward and simply edit it so the ip is the same as ur IPV4 on the cmd

hope this helps :D[/quote]
no figured it out went to my duc and had to refresh it … i would rep u for trying to help but cant dont got 15 rep yet.

item.title: Wont connect
item.dc:creator: @fleminmj01 fleminmj01
item.description:
@fleminmj01 wrote:

your ip adress may have changed. mine used to all the time. you have to open up command promp (cmd) and type in ipconfig.
find where is says IPv4. then open ur browser and go to ur portforward and simply edit it so the ip is the same as ur IPV4 on the cmd

hope this helps
